INSERT INTO `v1_090bb34aa14323c05c0750f1ed6cf60d4e0c724484619bf4847c022e8619dc54` VALUES ("", "", "", "", 1034501047, "", 1034501, 0, 91, "", "");
INSERT INTO `v1_090bb34aa14323c05c0750f1ed6cf60d4e0c724484619bf4847c022e8619dc54` VALUES (0, 0, "", "", 1034501048, "", 1034501, "vo_adv_1034501", 21, "", "vo_adv_1034501_003");
INSERT INTO `v1_090bb34aa14323c05c0750f1ed6cf60d4e0c724484619bf4847c022e8619dc54` VALUES (5, 1, "", 1, 1034501049, 0, 1034501, 103411, 11, 0, "だから、今日は麦しゅわは封印よ。\n麦しゅわもありの大人な誕生日は、\nキミが大人になってから……ね？");
INSERT INTO `v1_090bb34aa14323c05c0750f1ed6cf60d4e0c724484619bf4847c022e8619dc54` VALUES ("", "", "", "", 1034501050, "", 1034501, 0, 91, "", "");
